{"ayat_mp3":"https://everyayah.com/data/Alafasy_128kbps/002203.mp3","arabic":"۞وَٱذۡكُرُواْ ٱللَّهَ فِيٓ أَيَّامٖ مَّعۡدُودَٰتٖۚ فَمَن تَعَجَّلَ فِي يَوۡمَيۡنِ فَلَآ إِثۡمَ عَلَيۡهِ وَمَن تَأَخَّرَ فَلَآ إِثۡمَ عَلَيۡهِۖ لِمَنِ ٱتَّقَىٰۗ وَٱتَّقُواْ ٱللَّهَ وَٱعۡلَمُوٓاْ أَنَّكُمۡ إِلَيۡهِ تُحۡشَرُونَ","bengali":"আর স্মরণ কর আল্লাহকে নির্দিষ্ট সংখ্যক কয়েকটি দিনে। অতঃপর যে লোক তাড়াহুড়া করে চলে যাবে শুধু দু, দিনের মধ্যে, তার জন্যে কোন পাপ নেই। আর যে লোক থেকে যাবে তাঁর উপর কোন পাপ নেই, অবশ্য যারা ভয় করে। আর তোমরা আল্লাহকে ভয় করতে থাক এবং নিশ্চিত জেনে রাখ, তোমরা সবাই তার সামনে সমবেত হবে।","english":"And remember Allah during the appointed Days. But whosoever hastens to leave in two days, there is no sin on him and whosoever stays on, there is no sin on him, if his aim is to do good and obey Allah (fear Him), and know that you will surely be gathered unto Him","wbw":[{"bengali":"এবং তোমরা স্মরণ করো","english":"And remember","en_t":"wa-udh'kuru","arabic":"۞وَٱذۡكُرُواْ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_203_001.mp3"},{"bengali":"আল্লাহকে","english":"Allah","en_t":"al-laha","arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_203_002.mp3"},{"bengali":"মধ্যে","english":"during","en_t":"fi","arabic":"فِيٓ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_203_003.mp3"},{"bengali":"দিনগুলোর","english":"days","en_t":"ayyamin","arabic":"أَيَّامٖ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_203_004.mp3"},{"bengali":"নির্দিষ্ট সংখ্যক","english":"numbered","en_t":"ma'dudatin","arabic":"مَّعۡدُودَٰتٖۚ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_203_005.mp3"},{"bengali":"যে অতঃপর","english":"Then (he) who","en_t":"faman","arabic":"فَمَن","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_203_006.mp3"},{"bengali":"তাড়াতাড়ি করে","english":"hurries","en_t":"ta'ajjala","arabic":"تَعَجَّلَ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_203_007.mp3"},{"bengali":"মধ্যে","english":"in","en_t":"fi","arabic":"فِي","ar_mp3":"https://words